{"tid":1699780,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(請承認自己的無能) 幫全香港被罷工的事前準備細節及討論","createTime":"2019-11-08T07:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T16:05:58.000Z","uid":4322,"like":129,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bb000965f4cdd4fd93ea9cb98b51c6a0b674cb","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"周同學過左身 大家都好悲憤<br />\n但要明白罷工唔係個個有能力做到 <br />\n好多公司會秋後 因為呢場仗有排打<br />\n幫人被罷工都係可以理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想像點樣可以由一起身開始就幫人被罷工<br />\n大家早一晚早睡早起 6點好起身準備！<br />\n<br />\n1) 警鐘誤鳴 無lift搭 要行樓梯<br />\n2) 樓下每個巴士站有雜物 埋唔到站 條路就會更塞 （以唔好影響交通安全為前提）<br />\n3)上車個時數銀仔 站站有人唔唔好飛站 扮整親慢慢上落車<br />\n4) 不斷過對面來回搭車loop到夠鐘<br />\n5) 假日司機都要全體出動 超守法揸車 慢過平時揸 做足考車個時規矩 路口睇真望真先出去<br />\n6)高速公路/tunnel扮爆呔死火塞路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要路面一塞 人就會去鐵 鐵就頂唔順 因為本身已經overloaded in peak hours</span></strong></span> <br />\n但基於鐵太多cam &amp; food panda 建議玩得小心d <br />\n<br />\n1) 戴口罩喪咳扮暈拉手制唔犯法 <br />\n2) 唔小心跌野落路軌唔犯法 <br />\n3) 同站長講好似有人墜軌唔犯法<br />\n4)遲左落車畀門夾唔犯法 <br />\n5) 個袋夾到個門唔犯法 <br />\n只要每個站每卡都有人輪住做 架車想順利開都難 <br />\n6)係車站食煙令警鐘誤鳴淨係罰錢唔使拉<br />\n7)頭站倒瀉野等人唔敢上車唔犯法<br />\n*千萬唔好襯無人無狗係大站放雞尾酒<br />\n*千萬唔好Tunnel快閃RB<br />\n*千萬放完RB再放埋屎魔法/腐爛野落去 無普通人敢掂架<br />\n<br />\n重申我知罷工係合法權利<br />\n但請體諒埋好多人都想被罷工<br />\n我地好願意配合！<br />\n咁多人上過街支持我地 <br />\n只要做好文宣 決定好時間 幫大家洗腦 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我地唔想再見有任何人傷亡<br />\n大三罷係我地唯一武器！</span></strong></span><br />\n大家明白點解要罷工被罷工 知咩事醒水打番公司話番唔到就得 又贏 <br />\n大大聲係車上面講 &ldquo;屌落車食早餐喇望 有排玩呀佢地&rdquo; 攪掂!<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e559ccba1ef8c4229ad3d5e26b92080faa8b7c81","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"2c6111291504d236774a9d42a6125cc0ef8f88c8","tid":1699780,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">被罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"48abc1843426bd04a9640a44c6afb00465299a9b","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"dc059ba1d5bdbf95c5e2e697df7593d2cb366ee7","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"b0e193f97789b3b999e0ab39471d1863102fafeb","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"cfc5bead6b3a8ba019245bd0b89cfde730ecdafe","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"3a09a4ab863d9e420a67039ca37d517cd8303637","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"5f02d48e4621cf50a9955f5c3619732037b41462","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"d4ec2459959ed4463a40ed423d2d3ff9076ae9c6","tid":1699780,"uid":205631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁!!"},{"pid":"1fe0d25ce1e9e4093c3402c2fd24a35bee6a154d","tid":1699780,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"cbad799a88ada1b8f24bd7c6273cceacfc9f3d86","tid":1699780,"uid":59799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"推！大家謹記！早啲起身！"},{"pid":"bc414f2dd4cd3f1f4bb3cc20d6659b2b2bb22324","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"b8824a3ebb569ea49e2ebfae2f7d993b0eee2053","tid":1699780,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"